column4: On the wiki I'm on step 2.2.2.3, loading the new module.  It seems like 'sudo depmod -a' is working fine, but when I tried 'sudo modprobe ndiswrapper', it hangs.  I checked the log and it said loadndiswrapper failed to load, any ideas?
Is there one with less people?
